STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Tacari Trevon MINIFEE, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1661 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Tacari Minifee appeals his conviction and sentences for first-degree murder and first-degree robbery. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
